{"tid":2345644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉門胡塞軍宣佈： 我們已輕易擊落 解放軍彩虹4型無人機","createTime":"2020-12-29T16:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T14:17:26.000Z","uid":54373,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"98464941199603dd2a7e987c51436ce29f0aeaae","tid":2345644,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5362/d5362147.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5362%2Fd5362147.jpg&h=3c0fdd49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲沙烏地阿拉伯的彩虹4型無人機，被胡塞軍擊毀。（圖／擷取自fighterjetsworld）<br />\n<br />\n實習記者陳培鈞／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n葉門的胡塞軍發言人薩里（Yehia Sarie）21日表示，他們在馬里布省（Marib）的馬達加爾（Medghal）地區，成功擊落1架沙烏地阿拉伯的彩虹4型（Rainbow-4）攻擊型無人機，還釋出影片，但尚未確定其真實性。彩虹4型攻擊型無人機由中國航天科技集團公司（CASC）生產，並在2017年賣給沙烏地阿拉伯。<br />\n<br />\n根據《戰機世界》（Fighter Jets World）報導，胡塞軍發言人薩里在21日表示，無人機在馬里布省的馬達加爾地區被防空導彈武器擊落，他還強調，擊落的是中國製的彩虹4型無人機。胡塞軍也公開追蹤無人機的影像，但真實性有待查證。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，胡塞軍搭載了簡易防空導彈系統，並使用西方商業熱成像設備進行搜索和追蹤，成功捕獲目標後，引導頭就會啟動，並發射導彈追蹤目標將其摧毀；該系統曾成功擊落沙烏地阿拉伯的F-15鷹式戰鬥機和彩虹無人機。<br />\n<br />\n彩虹4型無人機由中國航天科技集團公司（CASC）生產，不僅配備可旋轉的光電轉塔，還使用合成孔徑雷達，平時可攜帶四個機翼下掛架，最大載重345公斤。此外，還可以攜帶300公斤以上的彈藥，像是AR-1激光制導的空地導彈、TG-100激光慣性制導炸彈、FT-9 50公斤的GPS全球定位制導炸彈和普通彈藥；可用來執行海上高空偵察及空對地打擊任務，武器射程可達5000公尺。<br />\n<br />\n沙烏地阿拉伯與中國在2017年簽署，一筆價值650億美元的出口合作，引進中國航天科技集團「彩虹-4A」無人機及全套技術和生產線。"},{"pid":"cff01005dabd9d8a5d7db2d488754d482bcc9f48","tid":2345644,"uid":54373,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:06:25.000Z","msg":"據了解，胡塞軍搭載了簡易防空導彈系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e0c69ed55f1973b3219e6f4c9b84686b9dd939","tid":2345644,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />垃圾軍力國家"},{"pid":"695cc6ca823ed7c715df2993cd3b34abf89b6db5","tid":2345644,"uid":284432,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:09:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1be5fdbb51769645e4ef42f019660bb4cc77fcd","tid":2345644,"uid":84102,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:10:16.000Z","msg":"彩虹4型無人機去咗彩虹橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/vampire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3176988a18977da16e782669cef0b8f7805530c","tid":2345644,"uid":199669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"胡塞武裝伊朗d人黎<br />\n做咩內哄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fcab534340fa1a957080cd93545f819821cf169","tid":2345644,"uid":30145,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cff01005dabd9d8a5d7db2d488754d482bcc9f48","tid":2345644,"uid":54373,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:06:25.000Z","msg":"據了解，胡塞軍搭載了簡易防空導彈系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:11:12.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">該系統曾成功擊落沙烏地阿拉伯的F-15鷹式戰鬥機和彩虹無人機。\n</code></pre><br />\n F15都一樣擊落到 似沙特本身自己都廢廢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0489c973736c735ef9b3c0435d59032076e16a","tid":2345644,"uid":61082,"like":3,"dislike"